title: Big Dawgs

description.plain:
“Big Dawgs” is a standalone single by rising rapper Hanumankind produced by Kalmi, who is known for producing several tracks for him such as the ones off of his EP, Surface Level.

The song started to gain notable traction when popular streamers such as iShowSpeed, and No Life Shaq reacted to the music video giving it positive appreciation. Additionally, the song gained more traction through popular social media platforms such as Tiktok and Instagram.

During the tracking week ending August 10, 2024, the song debuted at #57 on the Billboard Hot 100. The song marks both Hanumankind and Kalmi’s first appearance on the chart.
